# 🏠 RoomHub — Backend API

A RESTful API for the RoomHub room rental marketplace, built with **Laravel 13** and **PHP 8.3+**.

---

## 📋 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|-----------|
| Framework | Laravel 13 |
| Language | PHP 8.3+ |
| Auth | Laravel Sanctum (token + refresh token) |
| Database | MySQL |
| Architecture | Service Layer Pattern |

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

```
backend/
├── app/
│   ├── Http/
│   │   ├── Controllers/
│   │   │   ├── Api/Auth/
│   │   │   │   ├── ForgotPasswordController.php  # Handle forgot/reset password
│   │   │   │   ├── LoginController.php            # User login & logout
│   │   │   │   ├── RefreshController.php          # Refresh access token
│   │   │   │   └── RegisterController.php         # User registration
│   │   │   └── Controller.php                     # Base controller
│   │   ├── Middleware/
│   │   └── Requests/
│   │       └── Api/Auth/
│   │           ├── ForgotPasswordStoreRequest.php   # Validate send OTP
│   │           ├── ForgotPasswordUpdateRequest.php  # Validate reset password
│   │           ├── LoginStoreRequest.php            # Validate login
│   │           ├── LoginUpdateRequest.php           # Validate logout / update
│   │           ├── RefreshTokenRequest.php          # Validate token refresh
│   │           ├── RegisterStoreRequest.php         # Validate registration
│   │           └── RegisterUpdateRequest.php        # Validate profile update
│   ├── Models/
│   │   ├── RefreshToken.php                         # Refresh token model
│   │   └── User.php                                 # User model
│   ├── Providers/
│   ├── Service/
│   │   └── Api/
