## 🌱 Environment Variables

```env
APP_NAME=RoomHub
APP_ENV=local
APP_URL=http://localhost:8000

DB_CONNECTION=mysql
DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=roomhub
DB_USERNAME=root
DB_PASSWORD=

SANCTUM_STATEFUL_DOMAINS=localhost:3000

# (Optional) Google OAuth
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:3000/auth/callback
```

